    jsr tx_econet_abort                                               ; 8afd: 20 40 ad     @.      ; Initialise workspace area
; ***************************************************************************************
; Scan keyboard for remote-operation keys
;
; Uses OSBYTE &7A with Y=&7F to check whether remote-operation keys (&CE..&CF) are
; currently pressed. If neither key is detected, clears svc_state and nfs_workspace to
; zero via the clear_svc_and_ws entry point (also used directly by cmd_roff). Called by
; check_escape.
;
; X is saved into nfs_workspace across the OSBYTE call and restored each iteration – the
; loop reuses A as the key-code counter without needing X. clear_svc_and_ws is also
; entered directly (label) by cmd_roff with no register pre-conditions.
;
; On Entry:
;     X: preserved by being saved to nfs_workspace and reloaded each iteration (no other preconditions)
;
; On Exit:
